result.title: Need A Coach.
result.content:
Hello dear friends! New, 2015 year — it is a time for doing some good things, isn't it? =)

As you can understand from my nick-name — my aim is to find a coach. I want to improve my programming skills. What I mean in the word "coach"? It means, that someone, will tell me, what data-structure or algorithm to learn, which tasks to solve, sometimes will help with tasks.

I hope, that someone will help me ^_^)

Thanks a lot!
